<section id="faq" class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 font-heading mb-4">Soalan Lazim</h2>
      <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-primary-500 mx-auto mb-6"></div>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Jawapan kepada soalan-soalan yang sering ditanya tentang perkhidmatan kami.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <!-- FAQ Item 1 -->
      <div class="faq-item mb-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
        <button class="faq-toggle w-full flex justify-between items-center p-5 bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors duration-200 text-left">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Boleh pilih design sendiri?</h3>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary-500 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer hidden p-5 bg-white">
          <p class="text-gray-600">Kami gunakan design profesional yang telah dioptimumkan untuk bisnes kecil. Susun atur dan elemen rekaan telah dipilih agar tampak kemas, moden dan dipercayai — tanpa perlu pening kepala pilih sendiri.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- FAQ Item 2 -->
      <div class="faq-item mb-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
        <button class="faq-toggle w-full flex justify-between items-center p-5 bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors duration-200 text-left">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Boleh guna domain sendiri?</h3>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary-500 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer hidden p-5 bg-white">
          <p class="text-gray-600">Ya, anda boleh guna domain sendiri jika sudah ada. Jika belum, kami sediakan subdomain percuma.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- FAQ Item 3 -->
      <div class="faq-item mb-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
        <button class="faq-toggle w-full flex justify-between items-center p-5 bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors duration-200 text-left">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Berapa banyak produk/servis boleh dimasukkan?</h3>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary-500 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer hidden p-5 bg-white">
          <p class="text-gray-600">Kami hadkan kepada kategori sahaja, bukan setiap jenis produk. Contoh: untuk bisnes bakery — kami hanya senaraikan kategori seperti Kek | Roti | Kuih, bukan setiap jenis kek atau roti. Ini bagi kekalkan website ringkas, kemas dan pantas diakses.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- FAQ Item 4 -->
      <div class="faq-item mb-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
        <button class="faq-toggle w-full flex justify-between items-center p-5 bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors duration-200 text-left">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Boleh edit sendiri nanti?</h3>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary-500 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer hidden p-5 bg-white">
          <p class="text-gray-600">Website dikendalikan sepenuhnya oleh kami untuk jamin prestasi dan keselamatan. Anda diberi 3 kali revisi percuma untuk ubah teks atau gambar (bukan reka bentuk). Fokus anda pada bisnes — kami bantu urus teknikal.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- FAQ Item 5 -->
      <div class="faq-item mb-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
        <button class="faq-toggle w-full flex justify-between items-center p-5 bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors duration-200 text-left">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Ada support selepas siap?</h3>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary-500 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer hidden p-5 bg-white">
          <p class="text-gray-600">Ya, kami sediakan sokongan selama 14 hari selepas website disiapkan untuk sebarang pertanyaan atau bantuan ringan.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- FAQ Item 6 -->
      <div class="faq-item mb-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
        <button class="faq-toggle w-full flex justify-between items-center p-5 bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors duration-200 text-left">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Website boleh naik ranking di Google?</h3>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary-500 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer hidden p-5 bg-white">
          <p class="text-gray-600">Ya, kami bina website dengan struktur asas SEO mesra Google. Anda juga boleh naikkan ranking dengan berkongsi website anda di media sosial.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- FAQ Item 7 -->
      <div class="faq-item mb-4 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
        <button class="faq-toggle w-full flex justify-between items-center p-5 bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors duration-200 text-left">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Boleh buat kedai online (e-commerce)?</h3>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-primary-500 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer hidden p-5 bg-white">
          <p class="text-gray-600">Untuk pakej ini, kami hanya sediakan paparan produk asas. Jika anda perlukan sistem tempahan atau pembayaran online, sila hubungi kami untuk naik taraf ke pakej e-commerce.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>